956
00:40:18,577 --> 00:40:19,778
So, what should we do?

957
00:40:20,057 --> 00:40:20,818
We do nothing.

958
00:40:21,577 --> 00:40:22,657
Prince Yi can act as he likes.

959
00:40:23,497 --> 00:40:24,338
Follow me to the study.

